---
Maintenance Mode Plugin Help ---

[maintenance-options]
<strong>Maintenance Mode Options</strong><br /><br />
In this section, enable the forum maintenance mode and display a custom message to the user.  HTML is allowed in the custom message.<br /><br />
If you want to style the message, it will be wrapped in a div tag with id of 'spMainContainer', in a lower div with class of 'spMessage spMaintenanceMode'.
[end]
